# Local-dev pnpm lockfile. The Dockerfile uses `npm ci` against
# package-lock.json — leaking pnpm-lock.yaml into the build context
# triggers Next.js 16's "patch lockfile via pnpm" path which fails
# inside the container (no pnpm installed). Excluded so the npm path
# is the only one Next sees during `next build`.
pnpm-lock.yaml
